{"tid":404828,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(法律問題)將來本土派有人受襲計唔計何君堯煽惑他人作出襲擊行為？","createTime":"2017-09-18T11:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-19T11:29:21.000Z","uid":108201,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"731585bec280044f17c92c44b933584def668f81","tid":404828,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"如果戴耀廷寫下&ldquo;佔中&rdquo;文章都有「煽惑他人作出公眾妨擾」及「煽惑他人煽惑公眾妨擾」罪，何君堯講明殺人有無煽惑他人罪？？<br />\n<br />\n就算任何一個泛民或本土派人士兩三年後受襲都應該計得，因為雨傘參加者無睇過戴耀廷文章而佔左夏愨道都話受佢煽動<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b5c78fc7ab20098de5bf079539234635c278128","tid":404828,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:26:05.000Z","msg":"法律post無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18a7e86dd035b4d68229a79f5b29c764c44cc459","tid":404828,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T13:47:23.000Z","msg":"如果犯罪個個指出係因為佢而做出既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b21a325d7b73a3999f406854c61a978e5b2ed62","tid":404828,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:50:12.000Z","msg":"何君堯煽動人犯法、搞亂香港，好不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e46d639d60dd5b543c29d07ecc5516565d353d60","tid":404828,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T14:53:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04affe7010222ebacedb1d0810bc515bd7fe1384","tid":404828,"uid":47176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:09:26.000Z","msg":"有睇劉青雲套《消失的兇手》<br />\n都知道佢會好似套戲其中一個角色"},{"pid":"4451899d9df03fa0fb11741a4ca01d2297052927","tid":404828,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:13:41.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>第200章 《刑事罪行條例》</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第IV部<br />\n恐嚇<br />\n<br />\n24.禁止某些恐嚇作為<br />\n<br />\n任何人威脅其他人 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)會使該其他人的人身、名譽或財產遭受損害 ；或<br />\n(b)會使第三者的人身、名譽或財產遭受損害，或使任何死者的名譽或遺產遭受損害；或<br />\n(c)會作出任何違法作為，<br />\n<br />\n而在任何上述情況下意圖 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(i)使受威脅者或其他人受驚；或<br />\n(ii)導致受威脅者或其他人作出他在法律上並非必須作出的作為；或<br />\n(iii)導致受威脅者或其他人不作出他在法律上有權作出的作為，即屬犯罪。<br />\n<br />\n(將1920年第13號第2條編入)</span>"},{"pid":"1a9fb6ff60740a7398841dca08d03c485cb57270","tid":404828,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T15:49:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果犯罪個個指出係因為佢而做出既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把人屌鳩戴耀廷話根本唔係佔中<br />\n佔領運動同佢講既佔中係兩回事<br />\n<br />\n依家咪一樣入晒戴耀廷水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4b60af2f3b183923b04de17f3f14ab9fa3c8734","tid":404828,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-18T16:15:03.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第212章 《侵害人身罪條例》<br />\n<br />\n5.串謀或唆使謀殺<br />\n<br />\n任何人在香港境內串謀、同謀及議同謀殺他人，以及在香港境內唆使、鼓勵、勸說、試圖勸說或建議別人謀殺他人，不論其謀殺對象屬何種國籍或具有何種公民身分或在任何地方，均屬犯罪，可處終身監禁。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>(由1911年第30號第2及5條修訂；由1983年第64號第4條修訂；由1999年第13號第3條修訂)<br />\n[比照 1861 c. 100 s. 4 U.K.]</strong></span>"},{"pid":"ec1fbabe6ee6844bf48e86c9a5c26c7657a8c38b","tid":404828,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T03:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d2b629263a1806c81ad9921652c3763e9f451cb","tid":404828,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T03:41:31.000Z","msg":"唔告佢咪冇法律問題"},{"pid":"521816a272b4bd69b5dc92daa328488b50baa80b","tid":404828,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T10:25:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1444335fd7f875e0484ae11f9f250b83f776933a","tid":404828,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-19T11:29:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果犯罪個個指出係因為佢而做出既話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n大把人屌鳩戴耀廷話根本唔係佔中<br />\n佔領運動同佢講既佔中係兩回事<br />\n<br />\n依家咪一樣入晒戴耀廷水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係咁諗，雖然依家龍門亂搬緊，重&ldquo;奪&rdquo;就好暴力，要避免unhealthy wind has been blowing，&ldquo;殺無赦&rdquo;就要睇前文後理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果依幾日有本土派人士受傷或死亡，政府都可以話佢自然死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}